data.description:
MUST SEE this wonderful 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 2,180 sqft home, offering energy efficient solar, and a premium corner lot. Once inside appreciate the split open floor plan, soothing two-tone color palette, large ceramic tile in all the right places, and upgraded lighting fixtures and fans throughout. Fantastic eat-in kitchen featuring matching black appliances: gas cooktop range/oven, built-in microwave, dishwasher, refrigerator, along with gorgeous granite countertops and glass tile backsplash, a walk-in pantry, reverse osmosis water filtration system, and a large center island with breakfast bar open to dining area and great room, making the perfect setup to entertain family and friends. From the spacious inviting great room, you have convenient access to the backyard to extend your entertaining space. Step on out to the extended covered patio and marvel at the expansive area awaiting your backyard dream oasis, low maintenance synthetic grass, and only single story homes nearby, giving way for some incredible sky views. Back inside, wander over to the primary bedroom with ensuite bathroom highlighting dual sinks, garden tub separate from glass enclosed walk-in shower, private toilet, and a large walk-in closet. The other three bedrooms, laundry room, and 2-car garage round out this incredible floor plan, so start imagining filling the bedrooms with fun and laughter. Also worth mentioning, this home is equipped with a wash & dryer, extra refrigerator in the laundry room, water softener system, and epoxied garage floors (2021). Close to multiple community parks offering shaded playgrounds, sport courts, a swimming pool, and within walking distance to Desert Oasis Elementary school.

No smoking allowed. Tenant responsible for all utilities. Owner to pay for solar, tenant to earn solar credits. Tenant responsible for maintaining salt level in water softener.
